.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, horse, hamster, turtle
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, reggae, soul
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, lacrosse, tennis
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, quad-bike, snowmobile
 1. the owner of the hamster is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 3. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 4. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 7. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 8. the person driving the boat is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 9. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
10. the owner of the horse is not to the right of the fan of folk##8
11. the fan of reggae is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
12. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Pet      | cat   | turtle     | hamster    | horse |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | soul      | reggae     | folk     |
| Sport         | climbing | lacrosse  | tennis     | cycling  |
| Transport     | bike     | quad-bike | snowmobile | boat     |

